# Terraform
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
*.tfstate
*.tfstate.*
*.tfplan
tfplan
crash.log
crash.*.log

# terraform/bootstrap uses LOCAL state on purpose (see its README) —
# never commit it even accidentally.
terraform/bootstrap/terraform.tfstate*

# Node / general
node_modules/
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
dist/
build/
.DS_Store

